  "title": "Interior Design Consultant (Junior/Senior)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Looking for environment change for better career prospects?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Orange Interior is Hiring Interior Design Consultant</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Stagnant for being an interior designer or in creative line with only fixed basic salary or project commission only?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>We welcome <strong>Interior Design Consultant</strong> who're not only passionate in interior design but also driven to work as a <strong>TEAM</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Have more than 1 year experience but looking for the environment change?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>With our strong client base, you only handle <strong>genuine quality clients</strong>.</li>\n  <li><strong>Basic plus incentive scheme</strong> for qualified candidates!</li>\n  <li><strong>JOINING BONUS</strong> for qualified candidates!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage and follow up clients assigned.</li>\n  <li>Provide professional design development and budget consultation to clients assigned.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with project coordinator for smooth project management.</li>\n  <li>Create design proposal, concept mood board and space planning.</li>\n  <li>Initiate and plan out the project timeline</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Perks We’re Offering:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Remuneration package basic plus incentive.</li>\n  <li>100% coaching and guidance provided</li>\n  <li>Annual Income $60,000-$100,000 for achievers.</li>\n  <li>In-house project manager and drafter to support project and client management</li>\n  <li>Annual bonus.</li>\n  <li>Career advancement for achievers</li>\n  <li>Team work environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>The Ideal Applicant:-</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Have more than 1 year of art/creative/interior design/creative experience.</li>\n  <li>Passionate in design.</li>\n  <li>Provision in Sketch Up/ Illustrator/ AutoCAD/Photoshop</li>\n  <li>Openminded.</li>\n  <li>Goal driven.</li>\n  <li>Great work ethics.</li>\n  <li>Creative consultant or interior design background would be ideal.</li>\n  <li>Interior Design/Architecture/Art/Creative/Landscape background would be ideal.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>To enquire for more information or to express your interest, simply submit resume to us now.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Be part of our team of driven and dedicated professionals.</strong></p>",
